.Dd March 19, 2024
.Dt APPJAIL-LOGIN 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm appjail-login
.Nd Log into the jail.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm appjail login
.Op Fl u Ar username
.Ar jail
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Sy appjail login
utility logs users into
.Ar jail "."
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width xxx
.It Fl u Ar username
Logs into the jail as
.Ar username "."
The default user is
.Sy root "."
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std "appjail login"
It may fail for one of the following reasons:
.Pp
.Bl -dash -compact
.It
.Em EX_USAGE ":"
The command was used incorrectly.
.It
.Em EX_NOINPUT ":"
The jail specified in
.Ar jail
cannot be found.
.It
.Em EX_DATAERR ":"
The jail name specified in
.Ar jail
is invalid.
.It
.Em EX_NOUSER ":"
The user specified in
.Fl u
does not exist.
.It
.Em EX_UNAVAILABLE ":"
The shell for the specified user is invalid.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr appjail-cmd 1
.Xr login 1
.Xr sysexits 3
.Xr shells 5
